Text:
It's getting that time again, so I'm going to begin reseeding this file over the next couple of weeks.

Wld love to hear from any of you who d/l'ed it this past year.  Please reseed if you can.  Cheers.
It's been three years now, and I hope some of you I see leeching out there can hook up & get this beautiful song.  I'll seed it thru Christmas & a day or so beyond.  Blessings of the season.
